ACKHANDSHAKE -> node answers back its information possession information to a HANDSHAKE
INTEREST -> node to inform that it is interested in downloading a piece
CHOKE/UNCHOKE -> node to tell if it allows the node that is interested to download from it
REQUEST -> for a node to start downloading

div.div:
comm states
IDLE -> node i has not handshaked with node j
HANDSHAKING -> node i send HANDSHAKE to node j and waiting for ACKHANDSHAKE from node j
INTEREST_INFORMING -> node i send INTEREST to node j and waiting for CHOKE or UNCHOKE from node j
INTEREST_INFORMED -> node is has received CHOKE or UNCHOKE from node j
DOWNLOADING -> node i is downloading a piece from node j
UPLOADING -> node i is uploading a piece to node j
